      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite and version-controlled release notes consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 was used with documented QA procedures including regression test suite, version control, and release validation reports. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
    },
