      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate order-of-accuracy verification on canonical problems representative of rotating machinery flow physics.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy studies on Taylor-Couette flow and rotating disk configurations confirmed second-order spatial accuracy. Code verification activities are consistent with MRL 2 expectations."
