      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for the hemolysis index QoI across at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation study yielded GCI < 4% for the normalized hemolysis index at the design operating point. Achieved level 3 exceeds MRL 2 requirement, providing additional confidence in spatial discretization adequacy."
