      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation must be documented with sufficient fidelity to reproduce boundary conditions in the CFD model.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental dataset provides complete documentation of inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, fluid properties (bovine blood surrogate), and temperature conditions. Boundary conditions were reproduced in simulation within measurement uncertainty bounds."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
