      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index and pressure-flow curve must agree with experimental measurements within combined simulation and experimental uncertainty at all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index predictions fell within 15% of experimental values across all five flow-speed combinations. Pressure-flow curve agreement was within 8%. Both metrics satisfy MRL 2 output comparison requirements."
