      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which is the same geometry used in the COU. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range of 3–6 L/min at 2500–3500 RPM. Bovine blood surrogate viscosity matches COU fluid assumptions within 5%."
